#eNCA reporter Nqobile Madlala speaks to a resident of Riverlea, Johannesburg as the city continues to deal with daily power outages unrelated to #Eskom's blackouts. #DStv403 #SouthAfricaTonight JOHANNESBURG - Daphne Crook of Riverlea, who relies on oxygen to breathe, spoke to eNCA about her struggle for survival amid power cuts. Eskom implemented Stage 3 power cuts from 8am until 10pm on Thursday. WATCH: Stage 4 power cuts to last until 10pm The utility says it will revert to Stage two power cuts from Friday. On Wednesday Eskom ramped up to stage 4 rolling outages due to depleted emergency generation reserves. Watch the video above for more details on this story.